 * https://www.npmjs.com/package/syntax-cli
 *
 *   npm install -g syntax-cli
 *
 *   syntax-cli --help
 *
 * To regenerate run:
 *
 *   syntax-cli \
 *     --grammar ~/path-to-grammar-file \
